revision.text:
'''Johto''' is the second [[region]] in the Pokéclicker world. The Pokedex for this region contains 103 Pokemon from Chikorita to Celebi (which can be found in [[Ilex Forest]]).
[[File:Pokeclickerjohto.png|thumb|A Town Map of the Johto region]]
